# Space rings (space_rings flat ride): one tumbling ring (the engine spawns
# four). Disc in the X-Y plane, axle along Z, centred at the origin so
# animation.frames spins it and lifts it clear of the ground; a seat rides
# the rim and tumbles with it. One ring x 4 directions x 88 spin poses.
# OBJ space: +X forward, +Y up, +Z right; origin at footprint-base centre.
mtllib materials.mtl

